-- CSR to Construct Wind-Turbine Factory in Inner Mongolia, Xinhua Reports
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-25T07:08:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-25/csr-to-construct-wind-turbine-factory-in-inner-mongolia-xinhua-reports.html
 CSR Corp., a railcar maker, will
spend 750 million yuan to build a wind turbine plant in Inner
Mongolia, the Xinhua News Agency reported today, citing local
government in the northern Chinese region.  The company has signed an agreement with Tongliao city
government for the plant, the report said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
